The updates of COVID-19 in Republic of Korea 
As of Feb 27, 2020 
 
○ Compared to yesterday morning (09:00, 27 February, 2020), 449 additional cases are confirmed, which brings the total number of confirmed cases to 1,595 with 1,559 cases in isolation. 35,298 turned out to be negative and 21,097 are currently being tested. 





